## GITHUB PLAIN ENGLISH REFERENCE

- **Pull** = download the latest version from GitHub to your computer
- **Commit** = save a snapshot of your work with a description
- **Push** = upload your saved snapshots to GitHub
- **Branch** = a separate copy of the project to work on safely (not used yet)
- If Ryan is on a different computer, he pulls first to get the latest before working

