## OFF-PEAK SESSION: CHECK PENDING SPRINTS

At the start of ANY off-peak session (before 8 AM or after 2 PM ET on weekdays,
or any time on weekends), check PENDING_SPRINTS.md and surface the top item:

"You're in the 2x window. Top pending Claude Pro sprint: [name].
Estimated time: [X] minutes. Want to run it now or work on code first?"

Do not skip this check during off-peak sessions. The sprint queue exists
so no prepared prompt is ever forgotten.

